{"tid":914502,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"人越大 越唔開心","createTime":"2018-11-24T10:43:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-25T01:26:38.000Z","uid":177841,"like":58,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"ae05f7b396e2d59d8ab48e75abde9953fbc90f0c","tid":914502,"uid":177841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T10:43:22.000Z","msg":"人越大 越冇自信<br />\n人越大 越覺得目標遠不可追<br />\n人越大 越冇動力做任何野<br />\n人越大 越覺得咩都是是但但冇所謂咁<br />\n人越大 越鐘意自己一個<br />\n<br />\n以前既自己 好多朋友 小事都開心幾日<br />\n好得人歡喜 好多人願意同自己玩<br />\n而家呢<br />\n變到唔識同人交流 唔識打交道<br />\n連出街都懶得望人 寧願自己慢慢行 戴住耳機聽下歌<br />\n<br />\n好想有個人想自己講下經 冇負累咁過日子<br />\n但又唔想好容易依賴左人 <br />\n我知阿 人地話大個左回想以前開心既畫面 係代表你仲未成熟既行為<br />\n咁點解我會由以前咁active 變成而家咁唔識同人相處<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n好啦講完 唔知有冇人睇 唔緊要 當講左自己感受就得 反正都要繼續過<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8587eb69036100d4a907e6be47423ebf802f3e7f","tid":914502,"uid":210225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T10:47:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f928a72bbd2bf2fb93b4fcf4ff2db91a8438e231","tid":914502,"uid":216325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T11:45:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不能同意更多"},{"pid":"c6d7bbbb36c065c734eaa2f348b8d826e0dca7d2","tid":914502,"uid":222033,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T11:56:04.000Z","msg":"以為自己開post 完全係講緊自己<br />\n出街懶得望人 戴耳機聽歌慢慢行路 好中 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63b17025bdef5208ee4ff62b2edc520e9e2f7ce1","tid":914502,"uid":177841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6d7bbbb36c